gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Trail Blazers 114, Pacers 110
gameRecap.excerpt: The Trail Blazers defeated the Pacers, 114-110, tonight in Indiana. Jerami Grant led the Blazers with 34 points (12-18 FG, 3-3 3PT), seven rebounds, and three assists as Malcolm Brogdon (24 points, seven assists) and Deandre Ayton (22 points on 9-13 FG, 13 rebounds) totaled 46 points in the win. Tyrese Haliburton led Indiana with 33 points (11-17 FG) and nine assists. Portland improves to 5-12 as Indiana moves to 9-7 on the year.
